lead_paragraph: Edinson Cavani scored his 100th goal in all competitions for Paris St Germain in their 2-0 Ligue 1 victory over Angers on Wednesday, but the Uruguay international still cannot escape the shadow cast by his predecessor Zlatan Ibrahimovic.

headline.print_headline: Cavani Hits 100 but Zlatan Comparisons Persist
